1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:01,380
Yuki?

2
00:00:01,380 --> 00:00:02,210
Hm?

3
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:03,630
Your hand...

4
00:00:05,090 --> 00:00:06,300
Oh...

5
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:13,810
That looks painful.

6
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:15,720
I'll do the presentation.

7
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,930
No, but...

8
00:00:16,930 --> 00:00:19,480
Okay.
Let's have the next group present.

9
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,560
Okay.

10
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:29,610
Sorry to keep you waiting.

11
00:00:29,610 --> 00:00:31,360
Oh, did you turn in the report on time?

12
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:32,700
Yeah.

13
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:34,950
How about you? Is your hand okay?

14
00:00:34,950 --> 00:00:36,830
More or less, yeah.

15
00:00:36,830 --> 00:00:39,120
If you're not good at it,
you should've just told me sooner.

16
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:41,500
(I've managed to hide it until now...)

17
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,880
Let me see your hand.

18
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:51,260
Does this happen often?

19
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:52,680
Sort of...

20
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:56,560
Doesn't it hurt anymore?

21
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,390
It's fine now.

22
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,520
Huh?

23
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:05,190
Are you done touching it? Stop!
It tickles.

24
00:01:05,190 --> 00:01:07,110
Sorry, I'm just used to doing this with my little brother.

25
00:01:07,110 --> 00:01:08,120
Um, I was just...

26
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,690
Well, it's just...
I was worried about you...

27
00:01:09,690 --> 00:01:11,990
Oh, so you have a little brother.

28
00:01:11,990 --> 00:01:15,530
Yeah, he's still really young.

29
00:01:15,530 --> 00:01:17,620
Whenever he gets hurt, he cries and asks me to rub it for him.

30
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:19,050
(Not only has he found my weakness...)

31
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:21,540
(...but having him worry about me like this
makes my heart race...)

32
00:01:21,540 --> 00:01:24,250
(What is wrong with me...?)

33
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:25,460
Argh, seriously!!

34
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:28,090
Are you okay?
Oh, want me to make the pain go away?

35
00:01:28,090 --> 00:01:30,010
I'm not your little brother!
